id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a> インターフェースの<code><strong>onerror</strong></code>&nbsp;プロパティは、エラーが発生し、<code>EventSource</code> オブジェクトに対して <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/error_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/error\">error</a></code> が送出されたときに呼び出される&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">eventSource.onerror = function</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>evtSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onerror</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"EventSource failed.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>メモ</strong>: 完全な例を&nbsp;GitHub から見つけることができます&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/dom-examples/tree/master/server-sent-events\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"external\">PHP を用いた簡単な SSE のデモ</a>&nbsp;を参照。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ステータス</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/comms.html#handler-eventsource-onerror\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">onerror の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<ul>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.EventSource.onerror","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventSource/error_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"EventSource インターフェースのonerror プロパティは、エラーが発生し、EventSource オブジェクトに対して error が送出されたときに呼び出される event handler です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"EventSource: error event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"EventSource.onerror","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"EventSource.onerror","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/eventsource/error_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/eventsource/error_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventSource","title":"EventSource"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventSource/error_event"